587
00:33:42,906 --> 00:33:44,346
My dream was to make

588
00:33:44,346 --> 00:33:45,746
the best mobile game in my mind.

589
00:33:46,866 --> 00:33:48,826
So I joined the Gaishi Group
with great expectations.

590
00:33:49,826 --> 00:33:51,546
But after that,

591
00:33:52,466 --> 00:33:53,466
I never had the chance to get

592
00:33:53,466 --> 00:33:54,706
to the core content positions.

593
00:33:55,666 --> 00:33:57,666
I'd been looking for many opportunities.

594
00:33:59,906 --> 00:34:02,106
Although my colleagues
didn't say it outright...

595
00:34:02,466 --> 00:34:03,666
They just didn't see it.

596
00:34:07,986 --> 00:34:09,666
But after I joined Gaishi Unparalleled,

597
00:34:10,186 --> 00:34:12,186
I found your company was different

598
00:34:12,586 --> 00:34:13,906
and you were different from Zhao Qian.

599
00:34:14,906 --> 00:34:17,306
Miss An, you are one
of the few people in the gaming industry

600
00:34:17,306 --> 00:34:19,626
