and have a love for games.

601
00:34:20,386 --> 00:34:21,186
I really felt it

602
00:34:22,106 --> 00:34:23,346
when I worked with you.

603
00:34:26,066 --> 00:34:26,626
So

604
00:34:28,666 --> 00:34:29,986
I really want you to be back.

605
00:34:34,146 --> 00:34:35,906
Don't be nervous. Have some tea.

606
00:34:49,826 --> 00:34:52,146
(Chen Jiaxi agreed
to cooperate with us.)

607
00:34:54,746 --> 00:34:56,106
