No?

629
00:36:21,226 --> 00:36:21,826
Then I...

630
00:36:21,826 --> 00:36:22,986
We're leaving.

631
00:36:23,826 --> 00:36:24,146
Wait.

632
00:36:24,626 --> 00:36:25,626
Goodbye, Mr. Jiang.

633
00:36:26,666 --> 00:36:26,946
Goodbye.

634
00:36:26,946 --> 00:36:27,546
Okay, goodbye.

635
00:36:28,026 --> 00:36:28,266
Bye.

636
